+You are implementing Repository Interfaces for a Django DDD modular monolith barbershop POS system.
+
+This is STEP 3: Repository Interfaces only. No implementations, no use cases, no views.
+
+CONTEXT:
+
+Architecture: Domain-Driven Design modular monolith
+
+These are ABSTRACT INTERFACES (contracts) that live in the domain layer
+
+Concrete implementations come later in backend/src/infrastructure/database/repositories/
+
+Use cases will depend ONLY on these interfaces, never on Django ORM directly
+
+FILES TO CREATE:
+
+backend/src/modules/catalog/repositories/item_repository.py
+
+backend/src/modules/sales/repositories/transaction_repository.py
+
