+          output_field=DecimalField(max_digits=10, decimal_places=2)
+      )
+  ).order_by('created_at')
+```
+- Paginate manually with page/per_page
+- Calculate total_commission = sum of all commission_amount in full queryset (before pagination)
+- Return 200 matching spec Section 4.3 exactly
